{"id":"f923753a38155dc13d8ace2b6f577bbd4f7a707079a045075c66f91b32250066","item_id":"4fb951d550:0","text":"Solaris 允许你创建灯光并将其导出到 USD。"}
{"id":"97e156c277e3facd089ff4716bd90e883ad3fd9635136c77c4300c87c97e4334","item_id":"4fb951d550:1","text":"这些照明设置可以共享并导入到其他场景中。有关照明工作流的更多信息，请参阅 Solaris 文档。"}
{"id":"be618f46d8047a7659d552cc346df614ccfb936b326ddb6d28d78dbed88aa018","item_id":"4fb951d550:2","text":"Creating Lights（创建灯光）"}
{"id":"650c15b49561adc21636ca5362400ba96ca36e117a6fa22c58c5daf3c8869762","item_id":"4fb951d550:3","text":"在 stage view（舞台视图）中，添加 Light 节点，并从"}
{"id":"baaddf70fb5d432b8bd948ef91d6f910124a6d138edae4d5f000c4610ddc8eae","item_id":"4fb951d550:4","text":"Type（类型）"}
{"id":"4d0eba8b841b1b7c284ec1d107286e5c1034bd242e58f58e3a8687d41df26e60","item_id":"4fb951d550:5","text":"参数列表中选择灯光类型。PxrDomeLight 可通过单独的 Dome Light 节点使用。"}
{"id":"2fb894482c5b62f746ccbe9a3b6f8621ae7bfaa4d6b6437e51148b4a224f3730","item_id":"4fb951d550:6","text":"属于 USDLuxLight schema 的参数位于该节点的"}
{"id":"75425410734fa1cec691c4fc7d61bd9a35ef9699988d15bba748458044cf92fe","item_id":"4fb951d550:7","text":"Base Properties（基础属性）"}
{"id":"2c56a77ddafe41d7abb366bcadd5cbc24eba44bd35b6be8af44a523f42abc359","item_id":"4fb951d550:8","text":"Shaping（塑形）"}
{"id":"4aa9bfd2f175a94ad5a7cb321e1aea9790c73eb366a3415b47a00aeaa9fbf24a","item_id":"4fb951d550:9","text":"和"}
{"id":"4c764cb6248ef9337fc1c8769d4b74fc1d4c1fff6a9e8d00ca6753a560b3e74b","item_id":"4fb951d550:10","text":"Shadow（阴影）"}
{"id":"ec20d72b002b07af4e839ab80541ec2892971bd06c7da91c11b8cab79bed0612","item_id":"4fb951d550:11","text":"选项卡中。这些参数可用于多渲染器工作流。可用参数会因灯光类型而异。"}
{"id":"30938b0fb5c8ec18ad413a2f4b33ee1324fced838f1ef95552eae22611df7805","item_id":"4fb951d550:12","text":"RenderMan 灯光专用的参数位于该节点的 RenderMan 选项卡中。"}
{"id":"d8ea631951bcfb880072bfa6e55177557b87c861c5d9e27d3a345af2643f8a54","item_id":"4fb951d550:13","text":"Light Mixer 节点是查看和编辑基础灯光属性的便捷位置，例如 intensity（强度）、exposure（曝光）和 color（颜色）。你还可以通过创建灯光集合，同时控制多盏灯上的这些效果。Light Mixer 还提供了将灯光 mute（静音）和 solo（独奏）的方式。"}
{"id":"2bb40a6d27ed26fbbfd00b09c98af64eed7abb7676e151fced3cdd7ffbc88f07","item_id":"4fb951d550:14","text":"Light linking（灯光链接）"}
{"id":"8d0ce9329b67eb76e9a0e8bd3e2dbd56d1e2a2292dc0822c44c308851a06edcf","item_id":"4fb951d550:15","text":"可以使用 Light Linker 节点完成 light linking（灯光链接）。"}
{"id":"0df75bacdb54cc817481dab940a751993acbc3591d62847ca737178e2bd5b7dc","item_id":"4fb951d550:16","text":"只需将灯光或灯光集合拖到中央的"}
{"id":"4228aeb07c410ffc9d15b458bf7c2bf8d9dfa7af632f2c339e69f8cb54654da3","item_id":"4fb951d550:17","text":"Rules（规则）"}
{"id":"86418c07644ac4de6c3d4b0a6d3de09364d634acb8a8fc8f8ec0e002164ffa5a","item_id":"4fb951d550:18","text":"区域。然后将几何体拖到每盏灯的 on/off（开启/关闭）区域。类似地，也可以将几何体拖入 Rules 区域，并把灯光加入该几何体的 on/off 区域。"}
{"id":"e66e59fda9c6c75b0ded5247e784d3900c0ba3a98ee704d8932f2de0684ad641","item_id":"4fb951d550:19","text":"Differences from RfH（与 RfH 的差异）"}
{"id":"7f061bebd54fbf00971eae8289e06f7df9e223bf65328a3819d225a649f788d3","item_id":"4fb951d550:20","text":"Light shapes（灯光形状）默认对相机可见。若要关闭所有灯光的可见性，请创建 Render Geometry Settings 节点，并将 Primitives scope 设置为 \"All Light Primitives\"。"}
{"id":"9dad43cd256686f254110c62cce26377e52f993139d7c9a18aa6999b209b1cc6","item_id":"4fb951d550:21","text":"然后在 RenderMan 选项卡中，使用 Set and Create 覆盖该设置，再取消勾选 Camera Visibility 设置。"}
{"id":"4e3e72672ee9151baec563ce11d912848ce7049f809a5b14fae297cd1922fe67","item_id":"4fb951d550:22","text":"Solaris 不会自动转换你的纹理。"}
{"id":"7df727be44215bbc1ba485c70b838fdf4e48ff43296419cc6a84279dc6e6fb1f","item_id":"4fb951d550:23","text":"要在光源上使用纹理，必须先使用 Texture Manager 面板将文件转换为 .tex。"}
